logize for the rant. I just need to get this out of my system as it's the only chage Verant has made that has made me actually retire most of my characters except for my druid. I am truely for the first time seriously considering leaving the game. It's just not enjoyable for me to waste more time now on bank and selling runs due to this change. With my druid I have gate, ports & SOW. No problem but the rest of my characters are screwed. Well /flame off. Feel free to post your thoughts on this, thanks!!<br> <br></p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
